1. I'm hungry
2. I want pizza
3. I want extra cheese pizza with mushrooms
4. Call your favorite pizza restaurant
5. Ask how much it is
6. After hearing the price, call your second favorite pizza place
7. Decide pick-up or delivery
8. If delivery, give them your address
9. Place the order
10. Wait impatiently
11. Answer the door
11a. Be friendly to the delivery person, even though I'm so hungry
12. Tip the delivery person
13. Enjoy your pizza!